messages.messageBody:
I remember! I love the music from that game too! I really wanted to get it
but after seeing it, I decided the mature rating was well deserved. *I*
don't even feel 'mature' enough to play that game! LOL Great music
though...love it!

Jennifer



Speaking of music,

has anyone heard the music that comes from the cars in Grand Theft Auto:
Vice City?


My son was jammin' to the tunes, all from my jr high and high school years!
He really liked 99 Red Balloons, remember that German version?

Kelli~
